        <updated>2008-10-23T10:43:00-05:00</updated>
        <summary>There is tremendous fear in the air right now as business leaders across the country prepare their sales forecasts for 2009. And here???s why: It???s difficult to know what their customers are going to spend. It???s difficult to know what...</summary>
        <author>
            <name>mikecarroll</name>
        </author>
        <category scheme="http://www.sixapart.com/ns/types#category" term="Strategy" />
        
        
<content type="xhtml" xml:lang="en-US" xml:base="http://www.intelligentconversations.com/b2b_sales_intelligent_con/">
<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><link href="file:///C:%5CDOCUME%7E1%5CMIKECA%7E1%5CLOCALS%7E1%5CTemp%5Cmsohtml1%5C03%5Cclip_filelist.xml" rel="File-List" /><style>
